        "text": "I am so nervous about photos but Hannah’s kind and professional techniques made me feel perfectly at ease! She took our engagement photos at Garden of the Gods and they turned out amazing! I am so grateful I have these wonderful photos of us that I’ve been so excited to share. Hannah is really good at directing people, coming up with poses, and capturing the photos with incredible competency. I would absolutely recommend her to anyone in need of capturing your favorite moments!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2022-05",
        "text": "Hannah photographed our intimate elopement 10-1-21. I was very pleased with everything! Choose Hannah! She helped pick our location, plan our timeline, and photographed our favorite day. She not only captured picture perfect memories, but also captured our goofiness as well as solemnity while exchanging our personal vows. Extremely happy with our pictures, time, and money spent with Hannah!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2022-11",
        "text": "Hannah took our wedding photos and WOW!!! She did amazing work! Not only are they emotionally capturing the most important day, but the lighting and colors turned out perfect. She is so friendly and kind and so is Blake! He was really helpful and amazing all day!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2024-08",
        "text": "Hannah is a genius behind the camera and is the friendliest professional you never knew you needed. We decided to travel to Colorado for our wedding and she made sure everything was perfect and handled the craziness of the day. Always on time, approachable and made sure all special moments were captured. Having these memories to look back on is such a treasure. Look no further if you are wanting the best, down to earth photographer."
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2022-04",
        "text": "Save yourself some trouble and just have Hannah take your photos. Hannah has taken our family photos for 5 or 6 years now, and I could tell you she's a pro, she's easy to work with, she's personable- and that would all be true. But at the end of the day, you should probably hire Hannah because she captures the moment -- and makes us all look good at the same time. If you want to look back on your photos and feel joy instead of remembering how painful it was to get the photos taken, she's your gal. I will forever treasure the photos she has taken for us."
      }
